        "subject": "LU-2641 llite: avoid warning in simple_setattr with reg inodes",
        "message": "LU-2641 llite: avoid warning in simple_setattr with reg inodes\n\nCommit eef2380c (v2.6.35) added a warning to simple_setattr to\nbe issued if the function was called with an inode with a\n->truncate operation.\n\nAssuming the comment is correct above the existing simple_setattr\ncall, ATTR_SIZE won't be set and we can use our own copy of\nsimple_setattr that doesn't warn or call vmtruncate at all.\n\nSigned-off-by: Jeff Mahoney <jeffm@suse.com>\nChange-Id: I2501268f91638ab312beecd29890e168751d4e54\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b2_1"
    }
